    <briefdescription>
<para>Writer side of the lock-free SPMC ring buffer. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>There is exactly one writer per topic. The writer initializes the shared memory header, then writes messages into slots in a circular pattern. After each write, subscribers are woken via futex.</para>
<para><simplesect kind="see"><para><ref refid="classconduit_1_1internal_1_1RingBufferReader" kindref="compound">RingBufferReader</ref> </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
